snippet.title: Gaelco Arcade 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured directly off the OG Evercade handheld. This cart contains six games from a Spanish developer, Gaelco (not to be confused with Jaleco, a Japanese developer)

Games on the cart:
00:08 - Alligator Hunt
06:19 - Biomechanical Toy
13:38 - Glass
19:56 - Snowboard Championship
23:44 - Thunder Hoop
29:44 - World Rally
